text: Sébastien Flute is an French archer. He was born on 25 March 1972. Flute competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics, 1996 Summer Olympics, and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Sebastien FLUTESébastien Flûte == References == Category:1972 births Category:French archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for France Category:Living people Category:People from Brest, France Category:Sportspeople from Brittany
